snippet.title: Shark Wizard First Look Gameplay (Oculus Release)
snippet.description:
Shark Wizard is coming to Oculus Rift and Rift S for FREE in March!
We have made many improvements since the GGJ build and are now happy enough with it to release some updated footage to the public.

Learn more : https://www.bentlightindustries.com/shark-wizard
